Traffic Engineering (TE) Extensions to
OSPF Version 2
2003", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC3630.html", target="_top", tooltip="This document describes extensions to the OSPF protocol version 2 to support intra-area Traffic Engineering (TE), using Opaque Link State Advertisements."];
